column2: select S.ra, S.dec, S.petromag_u, S.petromag_g, S.petromag_r, S.petromag_i, S.petromag_z, W.w1mpro, W.w2mpro, W.w3mpro, W.w4mpro, S.oiii_#_eqw, S.z, S.h_alpha_eqw into mydb.wise_crossmatch_w5 from wise_xmatch as X join wise_allsky as W on X.wise_cntr = W.cntr join photoobjall as M on X.sdss_objid = M.objid join mydb.SDSS_gal_# as S on M.objid = S.objid_# join photoTag as Q on X.sdss_objid = Q.objid where Q.nchild = #
